1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,950
AI can help you run discovery faster.

2
00:00:02,450 --> 00:00:04,240
It cannot make bad discovery good.

3
00:00:05,140 --> 00:00:06,870
Discovery is broken when reps are

4
00:00:06,910 --> 00:00:08,230
pitching before they understand the

5
00:00:08,260 --> 00:00:08,630
problem.

6
00:00:09,180 --> 00:00:10,940
When they are asking surface questions

7
00:00:10,990 --> 00:00:12,720
instead of getting to economic impact.

8
00:00:13,540 --> 00:00:15,460
When they are qualifying based on budget

9
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:16,830
and timeline instead of whether the

10
00:00:16,880 --> 00:00:18,600
buyer has a real problem worth solving.

11
00:00:19,160 --> 00:00:21,250
Adding AI to that process does not fix

12
00:00:21,340 --> 00:00:21,490
it.

13
00:00:22,180 --> 00:00:23,300
It accelerates it.

14
00:00:23,860 --> 00:00:25,700
You get to the wrong conclusion faster.

15
00:00:26,250 --> 00:00:27,820
The fix is a discovery standard.

16
00:00:28,290 --> 00:00:30,080
What questions must be answered before a

17
00:00:30,130 --> 00:00:30,870
deal advances?

18
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:32,870
What evidence must exist?

19
00:00:33,460 --> 00:00:35,030
What does a qualified opportunity

20
00:00:35,110 --> 00:00:36,220
actually look like?

21
00:00:36,970 --> 00:00:39,190
Once that standard is defined, AI can

22
00:00:39,220 --> 00:00:40,000
help enforce it.

23
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:42,120
It can flag calls where key questions

24
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:42,820
were not asked.

25
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:44,960
It can surface gaps in the opportunity

26
00:00:45,020 --> 00:00:45,340
record.

27
00:00:45,950 --> 00:00:47,450
It can prompt the rep before the next

28
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:47,730
call.

29
00:00:48,350 --> 00:00:49,500
AI is a multiplier.

30
00:00:49,970 --> 00:00:51,930
The quality of what it multiplies is

31
00:00:51,990 --> 00:00:53,580
still a human decision.

32
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:57,090
Follow A-Gent for the agent-first GTM

33
00:00:57,150 --> 00:00:57,580
playbook.
